* Ramirez, S., Liu, X., Lin, P. A., Suh, J., Pignatelli, M., Redondo, R. L., Ryan, T.J., & Tonegawa, S. (2013). Creating a false memory in the hippocampus. [http://science.sciencemag.org/content/341/6144/387 Science, 341(6144), 387-391]{{Wayback|url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/341/6144/387 |date=20171018133842 }}.

